22:53.906 --> 22:54.927
I will pray for you.

22:54.947 --> 22:55.548
Is there anyone?

22:55.628 --> 22:56.309
God bless you.

22:57.610 --> 22:58.131
Anyone else?

22:59.312 --> 23:01.895
There's one person who has responded.

23:02.996 --> 23:05.619
Will you follow them to confess Jesus?

23:05.639 --> 23:07.801
You might have prayed that prayer, but not ready to put your hand up.

23:07.821 --> 23:08.382
That's okay.

23:08.422 --> 23:09.803
But why not put your hand up?

23:09.883 --> 23:12.466
Jesus, Jesus hanged on a cross.

23:13.090 --> 23:14.833
for you unashamed of your sin.

23:14.873 --> 23:16.415
He identified with your stuff.

23:17.156 --> 23:17.857
God bless you.

23:19.199 --> 23:19.860
Thank you Lord.

23:20.100 --> 23:20.661
Anyone else?

23:21.663 --> 23:22.544
You prayed that prayer.

23:23.626 --> 23:25.308
Just acknowledge you prayed that prayer.

23:25.448 --> 23:26.650
Or you want the prayer.

23:26.690 --> 23:28.332
You didn't pray it, but now you do.

23:29.554 --> 23:30.496
Would you raise your hand?

23:30.676 --> 23:31.337
God bless you.

23:31.417 --> 23:32.438
No, too.

23:32.719 --> 23:34.061
Let's pray that prayer again.

23:34.181 --> 23:34.722
Just pray it.

23:34.802 --> 23:38.107
Lord Jesus, I confess my sin.

23:39.629 --> 23:41.271
I come to you from mercy and forgiveness.

23:41.332 --> 23:42.994
I thank you that you died from me.

23:44.034 --> 23:45.136
Forgive me, nigh.

23:46.478 --> 23:48.241
I confess Jesus is Lord.

23:50.245 --> 23:52.108
I renounce Satan and all his works.

23:53.330 --> 23:55.393
I ask you to fill me with the Holy Spirit.

23:57.317 --> 23:58.759
Anybody else just prayed that?

23:59.701 --> 24:00.843
It hasn't been their hand up yet.

24:01.163 --> 24:04.549
You want to confess and acknowledge your faith in Jesus Christ.

24:06.011 --> 24:06.492
Anyone else?

24:08.496 --> 24:09.938
I want those four people.

24:10.466 --> 24:14.371
And anybody who prayed it and didn't acknowledge it to come over to me, I've got a big look for you.

24:14.772 --> 24:21.600
Don't worry, we're not asking you to sign any checks or we don't want your bank code or anything like that.

24:21.620 --> 24:22.742
We're not addressing that in that.

24:23.082 --> 24:23.963
We just want to help you.

24:24.264 --> 24:26.627
So come over to my left, you're right in a moment.

24:26.967 --> 24:30.191
Is there anybody he did identify as a Christian?

24:32.434 --> 24:38.642
But you don't really know this love of God and actually

24:39.010 --> 24:49.163
The love of other things, maybe some of the things I've mentioned, or Stephen has mentioned, has come between you and God's love.

24:49.183 --> 24:51.946
And you think he couldn't love you because you've messed up so much.

24:52.427 --> 24:55.611
You've burnt your bridges, you think, OK, come forgive me.

24:55.671 --> 24:57.613
I keep falling over again and again and again.

24:58.094 --> 25:04.482
But listen, why not tonight come back to the Lord, get over your sin and over yourself?

25:04.762 --> 25:06.144
He did 2,000 years ago.

25:06.204 --> 25:07.666
He got over you a long time ago.

25:08.802 --> 25:13.327
You need to get over yourself and you need to come to Him and get the help that is there for you.

25:13.347 --> 25:15.871
Is there anybody who wants to come home?

25:17.032 --> 25:18.213
Come back to Jesus.

25:19.515 --> 25:23.440
Just where you are, you once called yourself a Christian, maybe you still do.

25:23.500 --> 25:28.786
But people don't know what's going on and how far away you are from God.

25:29.106 --> 25:33.051
Maybe even started to doubt his existence.

25:33.071 --> 25:35.354
You're an internal agnostic.

25:36.015 --> 25:37.016
Are you even their Lord?

25:37.697 --> 25:38.738
But you want to come home.

25:38.882 --> 25:39.463
Anyone else?

25:40.404 --> 25:40.904
God bless.

25:41.625 --> 25:42.286
Anybody else?

25:43.067 --> 25:43.728
Put your hand up.

25:44.028 --> 25:44.689
Put your hand up.

25:45.670 --> 25:47.232
If that's you, just where you are.

25:48.754 --> 25:49.235
Anyone else?

25:50.736 --> 25:53.920
I know there's plenty in here like that.

25:56.443 --> 25:58.105
Anyone else, you want to come home.

25:58.346 --> 25:59.928
You want to know that love of God.

26:00.008 --> 26:03.111
God bless you.

26:03.131 --> 26:03.652
Anyone else?

26:06.916 --> 26:07.757
Thank you, Jesus.

26:08.098 --> 26:08.498
Anyone?

26:10.498 --> 26:16.545
Now listen, as I said tonight, come and meet me over here in the corner of my left, you're right.

26:17.205 --> 26:21.950
All those people that responded, they just want to help you a little bit more and give you some literature.

26:22.451 --> 26:25.094
If you need healing tonight, come and meet the God of love.

26:25.995 --> 26:29.979
The God who wants to touch you in mind and heart.

26:33.102 --> 26:36.746
Spiritually, if you're in bondage to something, you heard about Stephen's nightmares.

26:37.127 --> 26:38.548
Jesus can heal nightmares.

26:39.850 --> 26:40.210
Yeah?

26:41.090 --> 26:43.853
He can set you free and he can heal bodies as well.

26:45.134 --> 26:47.537
He can heal bodies.

26:47.557 --> 26:50.480
Why not bring it to him and see what he does tonight?

26:51.902 --> 26:53.624
Lord, I bless everyone who's responding.

26:53.664 --> 26:58.169
Thank you for those who responded for the first time, those who returned home to you, Lord.

26:58.189 --> 26:59.290
And we give you glory.

26:59.330 --> 27:00.331
We give you praise.

27:00.351 --> 27:01.472
We exalt you, Lord.

27:02.253 --> 27:04.996
And Lord, we just want you to have all the glory.

27:05.316 --> 27:10.642
Because you're the one Jesus who did the work for the pen you took.

27:11.042 --> 27:19.435
our shame, or thank you that more and more people are realizing that God, you're here, and you're alive and well on this planet.

27:20.597 --> 27:25.464
Lord, would you open even more ice tonight if others should have them taking that step?

27:25.484 --> 27:26.466
Thank you for what you're doing.

27:26.486 --> 27:30.612
Keep doing it, Lord, each night in Jesus' name, amen.

27:31.033 --> 27:34.618
Now listen, let me challenge you before I hand over to Joel, and then we'll close.

27:36.521 --> 27:39.666
Can you bring someone tomorrow night

27:40.674 --> 27:44.238
And maybe you brought somebody tonight, bless you, bring them again.

27:44.819 --> 27:48.283
That's somebody you brought, wait until somebody brings somebody, tomorrow night.

27:48.583 --> 27:49.805
This is where it works, guys.

27:50.405 --> 27:55.371
Okay, and you can comfort the tea, and the cakes, and the talent, whatever else.

27:55.932 --> 27:59.316
Come for all that, that's good, but bring somebody.

28:00.477 --> 28:02.119
Bring someone to hear the good news.

28:03.521 --> 28:04.562
All right, bless you.

